HEADWORD: Farrow
<hw>Far"row</hw> <pr>(f⟦acr⟧r"r⟦osl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>fearh</ets> a little pig; a akin to OHG. <ets>farh</ets>,
